      "title": "Seven foreign airlines reduce flights",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that seven foreign airlines have reduced the number of flights in this country by 56 (in a week) due to lack of refueling facilities and revenue generation problems.",
        "Also, two airlines have completely stopped flights in the country.",
        "Airlines such as Emirates, Qatar Airways, Etihad, Oman and Air India have restricted their flights."
      ],
